{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/List/Basic.html#List.dropInfix?.go\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">dropInfix?</span>.<span class=\"name\">go</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#BEq\">BEq</a> <span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">i</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span></span> ‚Üí <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span></span> ‚Üí <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> (<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Prod\">√ó</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span></span>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Inner loop for `dropInfix?`. ","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/List/Basic.html#List.dropInfix?.go","kind":"def","line":1028,"name":"List.dropInfix?.go","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/3881bc95874e5843b76886ea136f4722f1fa83cf/Batteries/Data/List/Basic.lean#L1028-L1032"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/List/Basic.html#List.dropInfix?\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">dropInfix?</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#BEq\">BEq</a> <span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">l </span><span class=\"fn\">i</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> (<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Prod\">√ó</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span></span>)</span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"`dropInfix? l i` returns\n`some (p, s)` if `l = p ++ i' ++ s` for some `i'` which is paiwise `==` to `i`,\nand `none` otherwise.\n\nNote that this is an inefficient implementation, and if computation time is a concern you should be\nusing the Knuth-Morris-Pratt algorithm as implemented in `Batteries.Data.List.Matcher`.\n","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/List/Basic.html#List.dropInfix?","kind":"def","line":1017,"name":"List.dropInfix?","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/3881bc95874e5843b76886ea136f4722f1fa83cf/Batteries/Data/List/Basic.lean#L1017-L1032"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/List/Basic.html#List.dropSuffix?\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">dropSuffix?</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#BEq\">BEq</a> <span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">l </span><span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"`dropSuffix? l s` returns\n`some r` if `l = r ++ s'` for some `s'` which is paiwise `==` to `s`,\nand `none` otherwise. ","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/List/Basic.html#List.dropSuffix?","kind":"def","line":1010,"name":"List.dropSuffix?","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/3881bc95874e5843b76886ea136f4722f1fa83cf/Batteries/Data/List/Basic.lean#L1010-L1015"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/List/Basic.html#List.dropPrefix?\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">dropPrefix?</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#BEq\">BEq</a> <span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span></span> ‚Üí <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span></span> ‚Üí <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span>)</span></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"`dropPrefix? l p` returns\n`some r` if `l = p' ++ r` for some `p'` which is paiwise `==` to `p`,\nand `none` otherwise. ","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/List/Basic.html#List.dropPrefix?","kind":"def","line":1002,"name":"List.dropPrefix?","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/3881bc95874e5843b76886ea136f4722f1fa83cf/Batteries/Data/List/Basic.lean#L1002-L1008"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/List/Basic.html#List.insertP.loop\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">insertP</span>.<span class=\"name\">loop</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">p</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span> ‚Üí <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">a</span> : <span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span></span> ‚Üí <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span></span> ‚Üí <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Inner loop for `insertP`. Tail recursive. ","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/List/Basic.html#List.insertP.loop","kind":"def","line":998,"name":"List.insertP.loop","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/3881bc95874e5843b76886ea136f4722f1fa83cf/Batteries/Data/List/Basic.lean#L998-L1000"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/List/Basic.html#List.insertP\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">insertP</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">p</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span> ‚Üí <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">a</span> : <span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">l</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"`O(|l|)`. Inserts `a` in `l` right before the first element such that `p` is true, or at the end of\nthe list if `p` always false on `l`.\n","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/List/Basic.html#List.insertP","kind":"def","line":990,"name":"List.insertP","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/3881bc95874e5843b76886ea136f4722f1fa83cf/Batteries/Data/List/Basic.lean#L990-L1000"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/List/Basic.html#List.isSubperm\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">isSubperm</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#BEq\">BEq</a> <span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">l‚āĀ </span><span class=\"fn\">l‚āā</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"`O(|l‚āĀ| * (|l‚āĀ| + |l‚āā|))`. Computes whether `l‚āĀ` is a sublist of a permutation of `l‚āā`.\nSee `isSubperm_iff` for a characterization in terms of `List.Subperm`.\n","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/List/Basic.html#List.isSubperm","kind":"def","line":984,"name":"List.isSubperm","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/3881bc95874e5843b76886ea136f4722f1fa83cf/Batteries/Data/List/Basic.lean#L984-L988"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/List/Basic.html#List.¬ęterm_&lt;+~_¬Ľ\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">¬ęterm_&lt;+~_¬Ľ</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.TrailingParserDescr\">Lean.TrailingParserDescr</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"`Subperm l‚āĀ l‚āā`, denoted `l‚āĀ <+~ l‚āā`, means that `l‚āĀ` is a sublist of\na permutation of `l‚āā`. This is an analogue of `l‚āĀ ‚äÜ l‚āā` which respects\nmultiplicities of elements, and is used for the `‚Č§` relation on multisets.\n","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/List/Basic.html#List.¬ęterm_<+~_¬Ľ","kind":"def","line":982,"name":"List.¬ęterm_<+~_¬Ľ","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/3881bc95874e5843b76886ea136f4722f1fa83cf/Batteries/Data/List/Basic.lean#L982-L982"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/List/Basic.html#List.Subperm\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">Subperm</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">l‚āĀ </span><span class=\"fn\">l‚āā</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Prop</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"`Subperm l‚āĀ l‚āā`, denoted `l‚āĀ <+~ l‚āā`, means that `l‚āĀ` is a sublist of\na permutation of `l‚āā`. This is an analogue of `l‚āĀ ‚äÜ l‚āā` which respects\nmultiplicities of elements, and is used for the `‚Č§` relation on multisets.\n","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/List/Basic.html#List.Subperm","kind":"def","line":975,"name":"List.Subperm","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/3881bc95874e5843b76886ea136f4722f1fa83cf/Batteries/Data/List/Basic.lean#L975-L980"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/List/Basic.html#List.traverse\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">traverse</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">F</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1 ‚Üí <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_2</span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_3}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">ő≤</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Applicative\">Applicative</a> <span class=\"fn\">F</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">f</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span> ‚Üí <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">F</span> <span class=\"fn\">ő≤</span></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span></span> ‚Üí <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">F</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">ő≤</span>)</span></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Map each element of a `List` to an action, evaluate these actions in order,\nand collect the results.\n","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/List/Basic.html#List.traverse","kind":"def","line":967,"name":"List.traverse","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/3881bc95874e5843b76886ea136f4722f1fa83cf/Batteries/Data/List/Basic.lean#L967-L973"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/List/Basic.html#List.mapWithComplement\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">mapWithComplement</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">ő≤</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_2}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">f</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span> ‚Üí <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span></span> ‚Üí <span class=\"fn\">ő≤</span></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span></span> ‚Üí <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">ő≤</span></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"`List.mapWithComplement f l` is a variant of `List.mapWithPrefixSuffix`\nthat maps `f` across a list `l`.\nFor each `a ‚ąą l` with `l = pref ++ [a] ++ suff`, `a` is mapped to `f a (pref ++ suff)`,\ni.e., the list input to `f` is `l` with `a` removed.\nExample: if `f : Nat ‚Üí list Nat ‚Üí ő≤`, `List.mapWithComplement f [1, 2, 3]` will produce the list\n`[f 1 [2, 3], f 2 [1, 3], f 3 [1, 2]]`.\n","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/List/Basic.html#List.mapWithComplement","kind":"def","line":956,"name":"List.mapWithComplement","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/3881bc95874e5843b76886ea136f4722f1fa83cf/Batteries/Data/List/Basic.lean#L956-L965"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/List/Basic.html#List.mapWithPrefixSuffix\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">mapWithPrefixSuffix</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">ő≤</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_2}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">f</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span></span> ‚Üí <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span> ‚Üí <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span></span> ‚Üí <span class=\"fn\">ő≤</span></span></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">l</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">ő≤</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"`List.mapWithPrefixSuffix f l` maps `f` across a list `l`.\nFor each `a ‚ąą l` with `l = pref ++ [a] ++ suff`, `a` is mapped to `f pref a suff`.\nExample: if `f : list Nat ‚Üí Nat ‚Üí list Nat ‚Üí ő≤`,\n`List.mapWithPrefixSuffix f [1, 2, 3]` will produce the list\n`[f [] 1 [2, 3], f [1] 2 [3], f [1, 2] 3 []]`.\n","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/List/Basic.html#List.mapWithPrefixSuffix","kind":"def","line":946,"name":"List.mapWithPrefixSuffix","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/3881bc95874e5843b76886ea136f4722f1fa83cf/Batteries/Data/List/Basic.lean#L946-L954"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/List/Basic.html#List.mapWithPrefixSuffixAux\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">mapWithPrefixSuffixAux</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{