Right'</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">ő≤</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_2}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span></span> ‚Üí <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">ő≤</span></span> ‚Üí <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> (<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Prod\">√ó</a> <span class=\"fn\">ő≤</span>)</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Prod\">√ó</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span></span></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Right-biased version of `List.zip`. `zipRight' as bs` returns the list of\npairs `(aŠĶĘ, bŠĶĘ)` for `aŠĶĘ ‚ąą as` and `bŠĶĘ ‚ąą bs`. If `as` is shorter than `bs`, the\nremaining `bŠĶĘ` are paired with `none`. Also returns the remaining `as`.\n```\nzipRight' [1] ['a', 'b'] = ([(some 1, 'a'), (none, 'b')], [])\nzipRight' [1, 2] ['a'] = ([(some 1, 'a')], [2])\nzipRight' = zipWithRight' prod.mk\n```\n","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/List/Basic.html#List.zipRight'","kind":"def","line":733,"name":"List.zipRight'","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/3881bc95874e5843b76886ea136f4722f1fa83cf/Batteries/Data/List/Basic.lean#L733-L743"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/List/Basic.html#List.zipLeft'\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">zipLeft'</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">ő≤</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_2}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span></span> ‚Üí <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">ő≤</span></span> ‚Üí <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> (<span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Prod\">√ó</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <span class=\"fn\">ő≤</span></span>)</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Prod\">√ó</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">ő≤</span></span></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Left-biased version of `List.zip`. `zipLeft' as bs` returns the list of\npairs `(aŠĶĘ, bŠĶĘ)` for `aŠĶĘ ‚ąą as` and `bŠĶĘ ‚ąą bs`. If `bs` is shorter than `as`, the\nremaining `aŠĶĘ` are paired with `none`. Also returns the remaining `bs`.\n```\nzipLeft' [1, 2] ['a'] = ([(1, some 'a'), (2, none)], [])\nzipLeft' [1] ['a', 'b'] = ([(1, some 'a')], ['b'])\nzipLeft' = zipWithLeft' prod.mk\n```\n","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/List/Basic.html#List.zipLeft'","kind":"def","line":721,"name":"List.zipLeft'","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/3881bc95874e5843b76886ea136f4722f1fa83cf/Batteries/Data/List/Basic.lean#L721-L731"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/List/Basic.html#List.zipWithRight'\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">zipWithRight'</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">ő≤</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_2}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">ő≥</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_3}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">f</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span></span> ‚Üí <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">ő≤</span> ‚Üí <span class=\"fn\">ő≥</span></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">as</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">bs</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">ő≤</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">ő≥</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Prod\">√ó</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Right-biased version of `List.zipWith`. `zipWithRight' f as bs` applies `f` to each\npair of elements `aŠĶĘ ‚ąą as` and `bŠĶĘ ‚ąą bs`. If `as` is shorter than `bs`, `f` is\napplied to `none` for the remaining `bŠĶĘ`. Returns the results of the `f`\napplications and the remaining `as`.\n```\nzipWithRight' prod.mk [1] ['a', 'b'] = ([(s