`tails l` is the list of terminal segments of `l`.\n```\ntails [1, 2, 3] = [[1, 2, 3], [2, 3], [3], []]\n```\n","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/List/Basic.html#List.tails","kind":"def","line":282,"name":"List.tails","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/3881bc95874e5843b76886ea136f4722f1fa83cf/Batteries/Data/List/Basic.lean#L282-L290"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/List/Basic.html#List.inits_eq_initsTR\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">inits_eq_initsTR</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\">@<a href=\"./Batteries/Data/List/Basic.html#List.inits\">inits</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> @<a href=\"./Batteries/Data/List/Basic.html#List.initsTR\">initsTR</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/List/Basic.html#List.inits_eq_initsTR","kind":"theorem","line":279,"name":"List.inits_eq_initsTR","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/3881bc95874e5843b76886ea136f4722f1fa83cf/Batteries/Data/List/Basic.lean#L279-L280"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/List/Basic.html#List.initsTR\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">initsTR</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">l</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Tail-recursive version of `inits`. ","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/List/Basic.html#List.initsTR","kind":"def","line":275,"name":"List.initsTR","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/3881bc95874e5843b76886ea136f4722f1fa83cf/Batteries/Data/List/Basic.lean#L275-L277"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/List/Basic.html#List.inits\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">inits</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span></span> ‚Üí <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span>)</span></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"`inits l` is the list of initial segments of `l`.\n```\ninits [1, 2, 3] = [[], [1], [1, 2], [1, 2, 3]]\n```\n","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/List/Basic.html#List.inits","kind":"def","line":265,"name":"List.inits","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/3881bc95874e5843b76886ea136f4722f1fa83cf/Batteries/Data/List/Basic.lean#L265-L273"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/List/Basic.html#List.lookmap.go\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">lookmap</span>.<span class=\"name\">go</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">őĪ</span> : <a href=\"./f